---
const steps = [
  {
    number: '01',
    title: 'Diagnóstico',
    text: 'Entendemos tu negocio, tus objetivos, tu público y el contexto actual.',
    icon: 'diagnosis',
  },
  {
    number: '02',
    title: 'Dirección creativa',
    text: 'Definimos estructura, estética, mensajes y experiencia con criterio estratégico.',
    icon: 'direction',
  },
  {
    number: '03',
    title: 'Construcción técnica',
    text: 'Desarrollamos el sitio, sistema, contenido o automatización necesaria.',
    icon: 'build',
  },
  {
    number: '04',
    title: 'Automatización útil',
    text: 'Revisamos, ajustamos y dejamos una base preparada para evolucionar con el tiempo.',
    icon: 'automation',
  },
];
---

<section id="proceso" class="process-section section-pad">
  <div class="section-shell">
    <div class="process-intro scroll-reveal">
      <h2 class="process-heading section-heading" aria-label="Lo hacemos en pasos claros">
        <span class="process-heading-line" aria-hidden="true">
          <span class="process-heading-mask"><span class="process-heading-word">Lo</span></span>
          <span class="process-heading-mask"><span class="process-heading-word">hacemos</span></span>
          <span class="process-heading-mask"><span class="process-heading-word">en</span></span>
          <span class="process-heading-mask"><span class="process-heading-word">pasos</span></span>
          <span class="process-heading-mask"><span class="process-heading-word">claros</span></span>
        </span>
      </h2>
      <div class="process-intro-copy">
        <p>Analizamos el contexto, definimos una dirección y construimos una solución digital alineada al negocio.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="process-step-list">
      {steps.map((step, index) => (
        <article class={`process-card process-step-row ${index % 2 === 1 ? 'is-reversed' : ''} scroll-reveal`}>
          <div class="process-step-copy">
            <span class="process-step-number">{step.number}</span>
            <h3 class="process-step-title">{step.title}</h3>
            <p class="process-step-text">{step.text}</p>
          </div>
          <div class="process-step-visual" aria-hidden="true">
            {step.icon === 'diagnosis' && (
              <svg class="process-icon" viewBox="0 0 160 160" fill="none">
                <circle cx="70" cy="70" r="34" />
                <path d="M95 95L124 124" />
                <path d="M48 68H92" />
                <path d="M70 46V90" />
                <path d="M38 124H72" />
                <path d="M38 112H90" />
              </svg>
            )}
            {step.icon === 'direction' && (
              <svg class="process-icon" viewBox="0 0 160 160" fill="none">
                <circle cx="80" cy="80" r="48" />
                <path d="M96 46L72 88L64 114L88 72L96 46Z" />
                <path d="M80 20V36" />
                <path d="M80 124V140" />
                <path d="M20 80H36" />
                <path d="M124 80H140" />
              </svg>
            )}
            {step.icon === 'build' && (
              <svg class="process-icon" viewBox="0 0 160 160" fill="none">
                <path d="M32 38H128V122H32V38Z" />
                <path d="M32 64H128" />
                <path d="M60 38V122" />
                <path d="M92 64V122" />
                <path d="M60 92H128" />
              </svg>
            )}
            {step.icon === 'automation' && (
              <svg class="process-icon" viewBox="0 0 160 160" fill="none">
                <circle cx="42" cy="80" r="13" />
                <circle cx="82" cy="44" r="13" />
                <circle cx="118" cy="84" r="13" />
                <circle cx="82" cy="120" r="13" />
                <path d="M52 72L72 52" />
                <path d="M92 54L108 74" />
                <path d="M108 94L92 112" />
                <path d="M69 114L53 88" />
                <path d="M55 80H105" />
              </svg>
            )}
          </div>
        </article>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
